posting_body: ['This very spacious 4 bedroom 2 bath ranch sits on a beautiful lot and has tons of square footage.', 'It has a large living room with a dining area.', 'The newly updated kitchen has freshly painted cabinets, new countertops and stainless steel refrigerator, stove and dishwasher.', 'The main living areas have new luxury vinyl plank flooring and all bedrooms have new carpet.', 'There are washer/ dryer connections, central heat & air, and yard maintenance is included.', 'The home has a deck overlooking private wooded back yard.', 'With a creek that runs at border of back yard.', '(There is a small apartment attached on the left side and a garage apartment off to the left.', 'Both are occupied).', 'No Smoking, No Pets, No Section 8', 'Utilities: Greystone Power, Austell Gas, $75-water and trash monthly (Paid thru PMU with Rent)', 'Rent: $1,795.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,795.00', 'Application Fee: $70.00', 'For more information on this or our other listings please call', 'show contact info', 'or visit our website at <URL>', 'ALL INFORMATION BELIEVED ACCURATE BUT NOT WARRANTED AND IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE WITHOUT NOTICE.']
